description:
In [this comment|https://github.com/mongodb/mongo-php-library/pull/783#discussion_r493568761], [~andreas.braun] pointed out that PHP 8's [{{get_debug_type}}|https://wiki.php.net/rfc/get_debug_type] can be used to replace the following:
{code:php}is_object($expected) ? get_class($expected) : gettype($expected); {code}
The above code is used throughout the library and its test suite. For earlier versions of PHP, we can rely on [symfony/polyfill|https://github.com/symfony/polyfill].

